== Escapes ==

=== 1.0 ===

Allows to escape XWiki Syntax.

|=Feature|=XWiki Syntax 1.0|=Result
|Escape a character|{{{This is not a \[link\]}}}|{{{This is not a [link]}}}

=== 2.0 ===

Allows to escape XWiki Syntax.

|=Feature|=XWiki Syntax {{velocity}}$crtSyntaxVer{{/velocity}}|=Result
|Escape a character|(((
{{{This is not a ~[~[link~]~]}}}
{{info}}To enter a ~~ character use a double escape: ~~~~{{/info}}
)))|{{{This is not a [[link]]}}}
|Escape longer text
(also see "Verbatim")|~{~{~{{{{ some **longer** text //without// formatting}}}~}~}~}|{{{ some **longer** text //without// formatting}}}
